{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1673906574.5785928", "card_id": "Q_579076003", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 425}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价剧版《三体》第五集？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "349 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/579076003"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ih635qtacp4MrEAMaCDkwOTY1MDIzIMuclZ4GMBY4kQRAAHIJNTc5MDc2MDAzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1673906574.579149", "card_id": "Q_579017821", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 496}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待爱奇艺被曝禁止 HDMI 连线播放一事？电视套娃式收费究竟谁之过？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "此前，爱奇艺限制投屏事件引发热议。起因是爱奇艺将黄金会员电视投屏限制在了 480P 清晰度，基本就是不可用的状态，而以前是可以进行 4K 投屏的。然而需要注意的是，爱奇艺还不仅仅是限制了投屏功能，甚至连 HDMI 线连接电视播放都限制住了。有网友反馈称自己在使用 iPad 用 HDMI 线连接电视时，界面都能正常显示，但点击播放却被弹窗「由于版权原因，此内容不支持 HDMI 连线播放」。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a323087487494807b78d8b358c650b2e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "232 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/579017821"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ih635qtacp4MrEAMaCDkwOTUyMTIxIMOJk54GMDo46wZAAXIJNTc5MDE3ODIxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1673906574.579813", "card_id": "Q_573857956", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d7